description: Feature Description : Verifying Login functionality for ITOpsAdmin
name: Login with ITOpsAdmin

steps.name: User with ITOps role renders the URL
user enters Username as "Itops_admin", Password as "qa123" and clicks on Login button

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

steps.name: "Admin" enters project name as "Automation_IB_24" in the search field
"Admin" clicks on Add new source button
"Admin" clicks on source dropdown and select a source
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" clicks on next SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
Success message for Severity Mapping must be shown in popup "Severity mapping details are successfully Inserted"

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

"Admin" verifies Delete icon of specefic Severity

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Add new source button
"Admin" clicks on source dropdown and select a source
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
Error message for creating duplicate source must be shown in popup "Source already exists"

elements.name: Adding additional source severity within the another source

steps.name: 'Admin' clicks on Add new source button
'Admin' clicks on source dropdown and select a source
'Admin' clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information

elements.name: Verify adding additional source severity within the same source
